# Obsidian workspace state (machine-specific)
**/.obsidian/workspace.json
**/.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
**/.obsidian/cache

# Claude Code local settings (machine-specific permissions)
**/.claude/settings.local.json

# Claude Code runtime files
**/.claude/history.jsonl
**/.claude/sessions/
**/.claude/cache/
**/.claude/memory/

# IDE files
.idea/

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Personal story content — only the skeleton is tracked, not actual stories
# Add specific story folder names here when needed

# Personal skill context — copy context.example.md to context.md and fill it in
.claude/skills/*/context.md

# Resource evaluation queue — transient files processed by cron
resources/tmp/*.md
!resources/tmp/README.md
resources/tmp/failed/*
!resources/tmp/failed/.gitkeep
